title: Summarize your last game.. with cat gifs!
body:
Yes, you heard me right: cat gifs.There are moments in playing League all of us can connect with -- but did you know cats connect with them too? 

Share your best -- or worst! -- League moments using cat gifs in the comments.

1) Asking the jungler for blue buff 
http://i.imgur.com/M3ZOx8D.gifv

2) When you get carried super hard
http://i.imgur.com/goZIZ8Y.gifv

3) Sona spamming abilities
http://i.imgur.com/Z1IHvlS.gifv

4) Stealing someone's penta
http://i.imgur.com/cf75loc.gifv

5) Getting your penta stolen
http://i.imgur.com/u9oTUBk.gifv

6) Jarvan trapping himself in his own ult
http://i.imgur.com/5cdhDUN.gifv

7) That feeling you get when you play Taric
http://i.imgur.com/AjvxSqn.gifv

8) Forgetting to Zhonya's
http://i.imgur.com/DDyzGwX.gifv

9) Actually *remembering* to Zhonya's
http://i.imgur.com/MZdpaZm.gifv

10) Failing a gank
http://i.imgur.com/XoNHYBM.gifv

12) No one expects the Soraka banana!
http://i.imgur.com/JC7MEff.gifv

12) Getting caught backing in a bush
http://i.imgur.com/fNazMYn.gifv

13) Getting ready to initiate a teamfight
http://i.imgur.com/C7EdqjG.gifv

14) When you’re too focused on CSing to notice a gank
http://i.imgur.com/wl1skSt.gifv
